Chasing...

212
00:19:30,487 --> 00:19:33,487
追いかけ
...after you.

213
00:19:33,687 --> 00:19:40,487
絆から愛に変われば
If a bond turns into love.

214
00:19:40,487 --> 00:19:44,287
染め上げていく
Staining it all...

215
00:19:44,587 --> 00:19:51,587
二人だけの秘密
...a secret for just the two of us.

216
00:19:54,687 --> 00:20:01,387
想いを込めた　言葉の強さ
The strength of words filled with feelings.

217
00:20:01,387 --> 00:20:07,087
信じて
Believe in it.

218
00:20:03,102 --> 00:20:06,402
